"pid":"dd716499de0eef51c7e7ffe539a42f14c98dd4cd","tid":1350184,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12801a543400cd85fd437a91f7615a4ce3d3c686","tid":1350184,"uid":171277,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"聽真d先<br />\n<br />\n似係普通居民想打白衫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好鳩傳   會柒晒"},{"pid":"fd554bdb81efd40c4ca354382ca5cdf387c85c53","tid":1350184,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"111c385649b36260804565a82acb08883e2ffbc7","tid":1350184,"uid":215935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d729008e7a30a40fae33df5578d87c9e3956fdfd","tid":1350184,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2x7DQUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2x7DQUV.png&h=791635de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好清楚我地武力升級有限，啲狗仲有好多武器未出，包括實彈同水炮車，呢啲傷害力好高，足以打散我地陣勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">硬撼對我地係絕對不利</span><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花是有用的，最緊要係打<span style=\"color: red;\">消耗戰</span><br />\n<br />\n警察只有3萬個，佢地冇可能短時間補充到（除非佢地搵國安扮警察，但係數量唔會多，因為好難落命令同埋組織戰術）<br />\n<br />\n而家夏天佢地下下都出曬防暴裝，朝早企到夜，對佢地身心都造成好大負荷，相反我地可以休息，可以補給，人數多到可以輪住做<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要拎住個<span style=\"color: red;\">主導權</span><br />\n<br />\n1. Be water，唔好戀戰<br />\n<br />\n呢個講咗好耐，但而家唔係講緊執生咁簡單，而係要變成主動一方，撚狗式遊走。<br />\n<br />\n我地逼佢地動員，但唔好引佢地升級武力。喺清場之前我地可以好似以前咁挑釁。<span style=\"color: red;\">當我地逼到佢地要清場嘅時候，我地就要毫不猶豫即刻散</span>，唔好戀戰。<span style=\"color: red;\">可以轉換場地，等佢地重新佈防，又或者留力去第二日</span><br />\n<br />\n總之我地<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀時間佢地休息</span>，雖然我地都會有體力消耗，但同佢地比我地會消耗得慢好多<br />\n<br />\n如果啲狗好似七一咁突然走曬去休息呢？我地就唔好畀機會佢地休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻升級，逼曬佢地翻出嚟之後又走，令佢地keep住精神繃緊<br />\n<br />\n2. 單一焦點，唔好浪費彈藥<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動都應該事先傾好，制定一個明確嘅目標。<span style=\"color: red;\">當是日目標達成之後，唔好即日觸發第二個事件</span>！好似琴日咁，噴黑國徽同臨時立法會宣言相衝，喺港島嘅焦點就去曬國徽度，我地又浪費咗一粒彈藥。"},{"pid":"5658822b4476cb45be1f2bed56acb8bfbc0adeb6","tid":1350184,"uid":23481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e04d52346c63f8739ffe4f75add2cd07f7fa5e6","tid":1350184,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"李漢民呀<br />\n點解仲未有人起到佢"},{"pid":"e3aa895bfd2f46e7b3580ce8c756e37ff18077dd","tid":1350184,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a10d5286b42348003eebd52b6748404408d42fe","tid":1350184,"uid":57329,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:20:23.000Z","msg":"唔駛片都知<br />\n正常班古惑仔點會打人打到落月台<br />\n黑警一來無路走斷正<br />\n一定係夾好晒先會咁<br />\n路人皆知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"但有實質証劇去支持係好事"},{"pid":"2f741bbd09205a170769da3641180c97d1100560","tid":1350184,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"呢班市民黎架喎"},{"pid":"e4225ac9012dfedd1c34f6b39ef9b20f9c901191","tid":1350184,"uid":134383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo